---
title: Rosemary-Dijon Lamb & Nutty Buttered Leek with Dill Potatoes, Lemony Greens & Honey-Sesame Cauliflower
description: Cook a tender and succulent lamb loin that's just right for a gourmet-style feast. With all the flavour of traditional roast lamb, plus herby roast potatoes, pistachio-crusted leek and sautéed lemony greens, it's sure to have you feeling satisfied with every delicious mouthful.
